	<div class="span8 offset1">
		<h2>Xylotone maker - alpha</h2>
		<p>
			Thanks for checking this out. It is my side-project while learning at Dev Bootcamp.
			Things are pretty early, so please be patient as things evolve. <br />
			The code for this project is available at <a href="https://github.com/1dlehands/xylotones">this github repository</a>. <br />
